data.value:
'Images and Waves' is processing tool for image and wave files and it was developed by Dragana Vučić, student of Computer Science at Faculty of Electronic Engineering, Univestity of Niš.
First use of tool is image processing which contains:
*Loading image, saving image, exiting program *Filters (safe and unsafe) - RGB channels, Sharpen, Gamma *Special effects - Pixelate, Edge Enhance *Histograms *Changing picture to 8 bit bitmap (256 colors) *Undo and redo actions, as well as reseting to start *Downsampling pictures by RGB channels *Compressing and decompressing by ShannonFano algoritham
Second use is processing wave files:
*Loading wave file *Sampling wave file *Concatenation of wave files
Note: All image/sound changing options will be shown/played after applying them. Blue spinning indicator frezzes when filter is applied and unfrezzes when it's done.
